SOP63_Node291.text:
買家是否有提供賣家宅配資料?
1) Open Chat (聊聊) for this order;
2) Check if the buyer provided all required courier details: 收件人姓名、收件地址、電話;
3) If all are present, select 「買家有回覆賣家宅配資料」; else select 「買家沒有回覆賣家宅配資料」.

SOP63_Node325.text:
買家購買商品後，是否有逾越鑑賞使用行為?
Open DMS > Returns > Case > Buyer Evidence and Chat，將證據與"不合理情境舉例P1~3"( TW /PH)中「不合理申退舉例」逐項比對；
符合任一不合理舉例則選「不合理情境」，否則選「合理情境」;

SOP73_Node202.text:
Open DMS > Order Details > Item List and Gift Info;
verify if the missing component is listed as a gift or only packaging (外盒).
If yes, select “是”; otherwise select “不是”

SOP73_Node57.text:
Open DMS > Warehouse > Return Photos. From photos only:
1) Visible defects/damage → '退回商品瑕疵/破損';
2) Fewer items than requested → '退回商品缺件/空包';
3) Returned SKU(s) mismatch → '退貨收到不對商品';
4) All requested items returned but extra unrelated item(s) included → '多退回商品';
5) If order is 直播單 and photos/chat cannot confirm item/amount → '直播單－無法確認品項/金額';
6) Otherwise → '其他'

SOP76_Node19.text:
確認買家購買商品後有無逾越鑑賞行為
1)Open DMS > Case > Statements/Photos. Compare with KB不合理情境判斷 ( TW /PH);
2)If no files or files are unreadable select"未提供 / 仍無法判定"，若商品狀態符合講義情境舉例，選擇"不合理情境"，否則選擇"合理情境"

